It generates a single unbox for the ctor call:

```
define void @"<Boxed>HelloWasm_Program_LargeArrayBuilder_1<System___Canon>__<unbox>HelloWasm_Program_LargeArrayBuilder_1___ctor_0"(i8*, i32)
